What are the primary types of ceramic susceptors available?The main types of ceramic susceptors are:
Graphite Susceptors (SiC Coated, TaC Coated)
Silicon Carbide (SiC) Susceptors
Silicon (Si) Susceptors marketresearchintellect.com
In which applications are ceramic susceptors predominantly used?Ceramic susceptors are primarily used in:
SiC Epitaxy and Single Crystal Growth
Si (Silicon) Epitaxial Growth Processing marketresearchintellect.com
